{"tid":1561594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】分化風應全部收皮","createTime":"2019-09-11T15:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:00:20.000Z","uid":197734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c8c4febf7e9a51518831597518b5513f23e236b","tid":1561594,"uid":197734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"我幾認同香港人有需要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不斷咁搵新既抗爭方式</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n登報、連署信、連儂牆、外國支援等等<br />\n永遠都會有更好更有效既方法<br />\n之前武勇日日都有揭政府黑材料既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非唱歌個影響層面係完全唔同<br />\n一方面可以有效地團結大家<br />\n但齋唱歌政府真係可以無視，當你無牙惡唔出樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁下一步點算好?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家熱門由屌武勇變左屌和理非<br />\n將首歌「定性」為國歌與否真係好重要咁<br />\n首歌唱完會搞到運動失敗好重要咁<br />\n屌完係咪就會有正面效果先?<br />\n個討論焦點根本可有可無<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家需要既係有建設性既方案呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係無大台，所以更需要大家<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用力去諗用力去討論</span></span><br />\n和理非完就到勇武接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武行動黎講其實係有必要盡快搵到新出路<br />\ne.g.再繼續用雷射筆玩警署個效果一定唔長久<br />\n到左某日<span style=\"color: gold;\">運動降溫之時就真係太遲</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不分化不割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"bd5832a1812f734723a3a13702167700ecf2adc3","tid":1561594,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 遮打見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span><